SUMMARY:English Conversation Class
DESCRIPTION:\n	Join this informal get-together for anyone who wants to 
 learn English\, improve their English or just listen to others enjoying 
 English conversation\n	Everyone is welcome\, regardless of their location\, 
 educational experience\, or background.\n	The conversation leader will help 
 everyone practice speaking in English through group social 
 interaction\n	Easy-to-read books in English will be introduced to improve 
 vocabulary and comprehension\n	Come for a friendly\, lively atmosphere and 
 get to know others who want to gain comfort with English 
 conversation.\n\n\nThis program will be held in the Literacy Room.
